FBIS4-26907 "drchi124_r_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-124 Daily Report 20 Jun 1994 North Region Hebei Reports Personnel Appointments, Dismissals Hebei Reports Personnel Appointments, Dismissals SK2806081494 Shijiazhuang HEBEI RIBAO in Chinese 20 Jun 94 p 2 SK2806081494 Shijiazhuang HEBEI RIBAO Chinese BFN [Excerpt] The provincial government decided to appoint the following functionaries on 1 June 1994: Zou Benzhen [6760 2609 4176] was appointed vice chairman of the provincial economic and trade committee; Zhang Baorui [1728 1405 3843] was appointed director of the provincial pharmaceutical management bureau; Deng Guohua [6772 0948 5478] and Ning Zhongyi [1337 1813 5030] were appointed deputy directors of the provincial pharmaceutical management bureau; Xuan Zhenfu [1357 2182 1381] was appointed deputy director of the provincial tourist bureau; Zhang Yingjie [1728 5391 2638] was appointed deputy director of the provincial national defense scientific and technological industrial office; Han Naiyi [7281 0035 5030] was appointed deputy director of the provincial water resources department; and Chen Benjin [7115 2609 6855] was appointed deputy director of the provincial public security department. It also decided to remove Cheng Guangwen [4453 1639 2429] from his post as deputy director of the provincial public security department, and appoint Wu Jiaxiang [0702 1367 7534] vice chairman of the provincial education committee. [passage omitted]
